Mugusigasira ibidukikije icyayi kimwe ni bindi bimera muri rusange bigira akamoro kanini mu guhanga ni ihinduka ry'ikirere no mu kurinda ibiza no kurwanya isuri ku misozi gihinzeho<ref>https://ar.umuseke.rw/unilever-yumvikanye-nu-rwanda-gushora-m40-mu-buhinzi-bwicyayi-i-nyaruguru.hmtl</ref>

